title: Sheet Pan BBQ Chicken with Roasted Garlic Herb Potatoes & Asparagus
description: A flavorful sauce is our secret for elevating a straightforward sheet pan dinner to a crave-worthy one. You’ll drizzle mustard-infused BBQ sauce over juicy chicken cutlets with garlicky herbed roasted red potatoes and green beans tossed in garlic herb butter—a family-friendly favorite perfect for any night of the week.
